    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1918-01-08T18:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1918-01-08T18:00:00-05:00" n="115"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d115">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Reinsch</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1918-01-08T18:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 8, 1918, 6 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your January 7, noon. What is amount of advance? Newspapers here report that
                    Japan has made a loan of fifty million dollars.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Lansing</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
